<title>UK: Polypipe buys Norflex for 2.9 mln stg.</title>
<headline>Polypipe buys Norflex for 2.9 mln stg.</headline>
<dateline>LONDON 1996-10-07</dateline>
<text>
<p>Polypipe Plc, a diversified building materials company, said on Monday that it had bought Norflex Holdings Ltd for 2.9 million stg.</p>
<p>A maximum further payment of 800,000 stg is payable dependent on profits during the period January 1, 1997 to December 31, 1999.</p>
<p>--London newsroom - +44 171 542 4019</p>
